	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />if you put a pal rom on an american board, will this work in american systems?  i have already done this, but my nes has the lockout chip cut, so i dont know if it works with unmodified systems.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
