	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Some games will work. Games that weren't also released in Japan or North America might fail because they do too much in the vertical blanking period. The game will run 20 percent faster. Complex raster effects based on CPU timing might fail.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


